# 🔐 Microsoft 365 Administration & Microsoft Entra ID Security Lab

## 📌 Overview

This project demonstrates foundational Microsoft 365 administration and Microsoft Entra ID security skills using the Microsoft 365 Admin Center and Microsoft Entra Admin Center.

It simulates real-world IT tasks commonly performed in small and medium-sized business environments, including identity management, user lifecycle management, security configuration, and helpdesk operations.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Create and manage user accounts  
- Configure security groups  
- Assign Microsoft 365 licenses  
- Implement Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)  
- Configure Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)  
- Explore Conditional Access policies  
- Perform helpdesk troubleshooting tasks  
- Manage full user lifecycle operations  

---

